{"tid":810454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家知道乞丐身上既係咩味嗎？","createTime":"2018-09-08T03:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T07:53:49.000Z","uid":31507,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0673510b16e18e376816bbbf4162ebc886a60a","tid":810454,"uid":31507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日番工搭巴士，開車既時候已經聞到有一陣尿味加怪味，見到旁邊有個類似犀利哥打扮既人，咁心諗好快到忍一忍，跟住就出事啦，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我旁邊既阿姐竟然頂唔順！！</span><br />\n起身讓座！！然後犀利哥就坐左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到最後我忍唔住嘔左落自己條褲度<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全車人都笑鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedf9a58aa267593d532bc9b81a23fe759571667","tid":810454,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"嘔落自己條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbf8654e6473548d0ca051dcc32c589d0d60cfb","tid":810454,"uid":6621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"好在我自己揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔會遇到呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f2476493b035a7d449ea6110b957a3ecc2ec24","tid":810454,"uid":31507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:09:13.000Z","msg":"唔講了，我要番公司洗褲"},{"pid":"4514cf896d1a842e4564cc59fa3a4b1145f51e78","tid":810454,"uid":157000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"我唔想同啲星期六都要番工既人講野<br />\n<br />\n利申: 番緊"},{"pi